rComments: Took Photo 1 & 2 and Digital Studio 1 & 2, His tangents are usually irrelevant, but still interesting. One concern is the repetition between 1st and 2nd year  courses. I was surprised that he repeated the EXACT same lectures over again in the 2nd year courses. Sometimes the explanations of assignments was unclear, it was hard to know what he wanted
Unfair prof, very bias towards certain students.

a very nice professor. he is very helpful and provides thorough feedback when requested. he is a charming professor and students are pleased with his teaching. he lets students think outside the class.
A great art prof.  His classroom discussions and readings are very helpful and so are his critiques.
Doesn't evaluate student projects with clear objectivity.  Disappointment as an instructor.
Great teacher. Enthusiastic about this course and a very approachable prof. He's always willing to help his students. I'm glad I took this course! Though I wasted money on the text.
